---
title: Cheesy Garlic-Herb Mushroom Burger with Spiced Kumara Fries, Pickled Onion & Slaw
description: Use nature’s patties – large portabello mushroom cups – in place of meat to make these scrumptious veggie burgers. Give them a little rub with our garlic and herb seasoning and top them with melty Cheddar cheese to create a dinner that's so much better than the local burger joint.

*Keep an eye out...Due to recent sourcing challenges, we’ve replaced orange kumara with red kumara, which may be a little different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
